#CHIP C352
#CLOCK 16000000

; C352 (Namco System 21/22) Basic Test
;
; The C352 is a more advanced Namco chip used in System 21/22 arcade boards.
; It has 24 channels of stereo PCM playback with 16-bit samples.
;
; Tests:
; - All 24 channels with basic sample playback
; - Stereo panning
; - Volume control

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 1-8: Left side
c4 .

; Channel 9-16: Right side
d4 .

; Channel 17-24: Center
e4 .

r4

; All 24 channels together (brief)
c4 & d4 & e4 & f4 & g4 & a4 .

r4

; Arpeggio across channels
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 . g4 . a4 .

r2

#END
